Brockmann is a skin for [PmWiki](http://www.pmwiki.org/), a wiki-based system for collaborative creation and maintenance of websites.

It is installed in the skins directory of your PmWiki install. Please see <http://www.pmwiki.org/wiki/PmWiki/Skins> for more on how to use it.

Brockmann is Copyright 2009 Gordon G. Brander
<http://gordonbrander.com>

If you like it, please let me know. I would love to hear how you are using it.

